        icon: {fileID: 0}
      line: As you dive deeper into the memories of the object, you realise various
        things.
  description: A beautiful hair ornament that Catherine Sinclair received as a gift
    after her engagement to the eldest son of the Sinclair family. It is decorated
    with small jewels and is worth a considerable amount.
  closeUpDescription: "On the back of the hair ornament, the words \u201Cwith sincere
    thanks, the Sinclairs\u201D are engraved. It does not look like this was a marriage
    of love."
